    <subfield code="m">Note that these stationary field modes, which are characterized by the critical (marginal) frequency (10) for the superradiant scattering phenomenon, mark the boundary between stable (âÏ &lt; 0) and unstable (âÏ > 0) resonances of the confined scalar fields</subfield>
