    <subfield code="o">28</subfield>
    <subfield code="m">It is worth noting that the near-horizon x âª Ï region corresponds to Ïy/r+ â -â [see Eq. (28)]. This implies eÏy/r+ â 0 in the near-horizon region</subfield>
