  <datafield tag="999" ind1="C" ind2="5">
    <subfield code="o">32</subfield>
    <subfield code="m">It is worth emphasizing again that the inequalities presented in (34) imply that the radial eigenfunction Ï is a positive and increasing function in the vicinity of the black-hole horizon [that is, in the near-horizon x âª Ï Ã min{1, H(r+)/(qQ)2 } region]</subfield>
